race.description: Cmaa Gold Coast 20Th Anniversary F&M Hcp (C1)
race.comment: Gollan-trained MEHRETU (1) missed a whisker first-up at Doomben off a trial win at the track. She further improved and has a 1.5kg claim and an inside gates. Strips fitter and rates to go one better. Stablemate IMMEDIATE (2) placed at Ipswich building on her 3L all-the-way win at Ipswich in Maidens. Peaks today and can make the finish. KAHLUA GIRL (7) was spelled off a Doomben Maiden win and was well supported at Gatton first up and may not have appreciated the tight turning track. Has the ability and can improve quickly. CAXTON LASS (4) is third-up and ready to show his best. Will get a soft run from the inside gate and deserves consideration. CHILPUR (5) resumed at Gatton and spaced the Maidens from the front. Fitter and is sure to give a sight.
